pet_information.name: Anubis
pet_information.description: Anubis is a loyal and energetic dog who enjoys long walks and playing fetch. He has a glossy black coat and a friendly disposition.

pet_information.name: Nefertiti
pet_information.description: Nefertiti is a graceful and elegant dog with a sleek coat and large, expressive ears. She is intelligent and loyal, making her an ideal companion for active families.

pet_information.name: Sphinx
pet_information.description: Sphinx is a friendly and affectionate dog with a distinctive brindle coat. He is gentle and loves to play fetch in the park. Sphinx gets along well with children and other pets.
